TASHKENT STATE UNIVERSITY OF UZBEK LANGUAGE AND LITERATURE NAMED AFTER ALISHER NAVOI

"SEMANTIC METHOD OF HOMONIM FORMATION IN UZBEK LANGUAGE" DISSERTATION ON THE SUBJECT
ANNOTATION
The master's thesis is devoted to the analysis of silence and internal speech in artistic texts.
The purpose of the work is to show more clearly the function of inner speech and silence in the artistic text and explain it scientifically based on the sources.
In the implementation of this goal, first of all, the situation of silence and internal speech should be studied in depth, review of the scientific research works on this topic in world linguistics, interpretation of the silent and internal speech of the heroes based on the literary texts, language-cultural, psycholinguistic aspects of silence, internal speech. the tasks of studying speech situations were defined.
It is also intended to clearly show the role and importance of silence and inner speech in literary texts with the help of examples.
Proposals and recommendations are given at the end of the dissertation.
